  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Non-interventional study to evaluate safety and efficacy of NOVOCART 3D in adult and
      adolescent patients with full thickness cartilage defects after the treatment with NOVOCART
      3D.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A 36-month post treatment follow up of adverse and serious adverse effects as well as the
      measurement of efficacy with the International Knee Documentation Committee (IKDC) Score.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
